data.description: Built by Pulte in Village Lakes of Palencia. Enjoy all the upgrades without new construction costs and build time. Nine foot ceilings, Eight foot doors,Recessed lighting, Crown molding, Tiled backsplash, Granite counter-tops, Master tray ceiling, Ceiling fans in every room this list goes on. Tiled living areas and carpeted large bedrooms. Office space located away from bedrooms.  Extra storage is available in the  laundry room, mud room and tandem garage.  Enjoy this open floor plan and beautiful view from the screened lanai. Landscape complete with irrigation system, extreme puppy picket fence, and home defense pest system. Amenities center located just down the street. Please enjoy the virtual tour . Additional list of upgrades available upon request.
